<h2><a name="01022011">1 Feb 2011</a></h2> <p>Austin, Texas - With a steady increase in activity surrounding the successful launched of the Marketplace, fresh to market KLECT Corp. has quickly added a new addition. The company's newest development - an intern from the University of Texas at Austin, Senior Communication Studies major and business certificate candidate, Elizabeth Bula.
<br/><br/>
Bula will be spearheading KLECT's communication efforts while assisting in software design support and operations. When asked why KLECT, she responded with a ode to the passion behind the business, "KLECT is more than a business venture. The passion that drives the ideas behind the company is unmatched. It is truly about the collectors, the passion for their collections and connecting community members from all over the world. Plus, I KLECT!"</p>
